Class TileConnectedTest

java.lang.Object
  jUnitTests.TileTest
      jUnitTests.TileConnectedTest

public class TileConnectedTest
extends TileTest

Tests if Tiles are properly connected. This is important since Tiles form a graph data structure - a graph data structure with one node is fairly useless.

public void setUp()
